{"tid":2034403,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"《數碼暴龍》CO-CO：激鬥！！數碼暴龍漫畫（1998）（單行本+完全體決戰篇）","createTime":"2020-05-25T08:18:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-14T16:10:01.000Z","uid":221062,"like":70,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"82a86a38d5765fd619777723dc7d51b6571212ab","tid":2034403,"uid":221062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T08:18:51.000Z","msg":"本地薑余遠煌嘅1998年成名作<br />\n雖說係喺外國網搵到，但據水印就應該係出自某陳年高登post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食住最近數碼暴龍個勢，俾大家重溫舊夢<br />\n&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/19rZyyd3idj5FjB9OvKUfr2nHgDHYPpbD?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fdrive%2Ffolders%2F19rZyyd3idj5FjB9OvKUfr2nHgDHYPpbD%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=g30fgRh1OaLpBbOto8aU3oeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=40819e37\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/19rZyyd3idj5FjB9OvKUfr2nHgDHYPpbD?usp=sharing</a><br />\n&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XaBtM0P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXaBtM0P.jpg&h=1079d5b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當年1997年推出嘅「暴龍機」（當時正名仍然係Digital Monster，並非Digimon）仲係走電子寵物路線，可以話俾同期嘅Tamagotchi（c. 1996）直接影響。由井澤宏執筆嘅《C'Mon Digimon》短篇漫畫可見，數碼暴龍當時好想將電子寵物同傳統寵物掛勾，甚至成為替代品，希望玩家可以同Digimon產生類似情感。據井澤宏本人喺《C'Mon Digimon》嘅序言寫道，《C'Mon Digimon》嘅主角<strong>加門健太郎</strong>就係井澤宏後作：V-Tamers 01嘅主角<strong>八神太一</strong>嘅原型，後來演變成《數碼暴龍01》入面嘅八神太一 [1]，淵源甚深。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GO3gbGu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGO3gbGu.png&h=07a3e751&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n八神太一原型，加門健太郎（右下二）<br />\n<br />\n初代暴龍機只有14隻數碼暴龍（黑球獸、滾球獸、亞古獸、暴龍獸、機械暴龍獸（病毒）；比特獸、海龍獸；惡魔獸；烈焰獸；飛龍獸；巨龍獸；鼻涕獸；豆豆獸；熊仔獸）[2]，後嚟先逐漸發展出其他品種。值得一提，呢個時期嘅數碼暴龍最巔峰嘅進化階段係完全體（「完全」，即係complete，英文翻譯Ultimate或Perfect，當年都具有完結、終極嘅含義；後來Ultimate又變成究極體嘅英文翻譯，所以有唔少混淆情況）。我哋今日熟知嘅究極體就係喺二代暴龍機Digimon Pendulum推出（個名已經變成Digimon，唔係Digital Monster）。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mr5m7fm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmr5m7fm.jpg&h=4d43cc4b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n初代Digital Monster<br />\n<br />\n暴龍機推出新機嘅時間極短，長至六個月、最短則只有兩個月（03/1997推出三代、05/1997推出四代），所以喺一年之間，數碼暴龍嘅數量已經增至70隻。時至余遠煌推出《激鬥！！數碼暴龍》嘅時候，暴龍機已經發展到第五代。第五代推出嘅黑暗巨龍獸（以及進化之後嘅機械巨龍獸）就順理成章成為咗《激鬥！！數碼暴龍》嘅主角，同搭檔馬子龍合作。<br />\n<br />\n由Bandai早期嘅暴龍機呢套漫畫可以見到初代數碼暴龍嘅設計。齙牙咧嘴不在話下，同時有別於渾然一體、左右對稱均勻嘅寵物小精靈（sor，講起數碼暴龍就好難避開同期嘅作品），數碼暴龍好有人工改造嘅痕跡。無論係充滿android色彩嘅一代完全體機械暴龍獸、二代推出周身釘痕嘅天使獸，都可以見到數碼暴龍當年充滿野性同混亂嘅設計，有一定嘅Lovecraftian horror元素。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lsp7inp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLsp7inp.jpg&h=09d4f939&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有指TV版數碼暴龍嘅進化路徑前後不一致，但其實Bandai由設計數碼暴龍肇始，一早就有多元進化論。暴龍機嘅設計，一開始就支援多重進化 [2]；由《激鬥！！數碼暴龍》Vol. 1 p. 3亦可見，官方一早就有「一隻數碼暴龍、多種進化」嘅構思；亞古獸唔一定進化成暴龍獸、甲蟲獸唔一定進化成比多獸 etc.。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BcTv0zi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBcTv0zi.jpg&h=ad60b834&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好啦，分享咁多住。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有關余遠煌，大家可以睇睇呢個01專訪<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2AZJ8pl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2AZJ8pl&d=g30fgRh1OaLpBbOto8aU3oeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=ae0724cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2AZJ8pl</a><br />\n<br />\n[1] C'Mon Digimon，英文版（<a href=\"http://www.mangago.me/read-manga/c_mon_digimon/）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mangago.me%2Fread-manga%2Fc_mon_digimon%2F%EF%BC%89&d=g30fgRh1OaLpBbOto8aU3oeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=12358d30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.mangago.me/read-manga/c_mon_digimon/）</a><br />\n[2] 初代數碼暴龍機進化路徑（<a href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20100615000049/http://digimon.net/city/gallery/ver1/v1_1.html）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20100615000049%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fdigimon.net%2Fcity%2Fgallery%2Fver1%2Fv1_1.html%EF%BC%89&d=g30fgRh1OaLpBbOto8aU3oeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=8327f597\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://web.archive.org/web/20100615000049/http://digimon.net/city/gallery/ver1/v1_1.html）</a>"},{"pid":"cecec2015b0d0a1c99f70a770f3de134308cd902","tid":2034403,"uid":221062,"like":2,"dislike":12,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T08:23:44.000Z","msg":"做咩負皮我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"427170807ecb4815d2267db604c1fd046cce693c","tid":2034403,"uid":15,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T08:30:52.000Z","msg":"睇返以前嘅數碼暴龍圖真係好有回憶<br />\n仲記得Coco一開始好似係送頭100隻數碼暴龍嘅Poster<br />\n整爛咗都用膠紙痴返好佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有Coco本嘢有浸特別嘅紙味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"667a22e94aac0cb8e7e0cfef8ded561204773d1b","tid":2034403,"uid":221062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"427170807ecb4815d2267db604c1fd046cce693c","tid":2034403,"uid":15,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T08:30:52.000Z","msg":"睇返以前嘅數碼暴龍圖真係好有回憶<br />\n仲記得Coco一開始好似係送頭100隻數碼暴龍嘅Poster<br />\n整爛咗都用膠紙痴返好佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有Coco本嘢有浸特別嘅紙味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T08:34:08.000Z","msg":"懷疑我仲有張poster喺度，又係黏哂膠紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原來咁有來頭咩"},{"pid":"f76e712075577633adfdd20a55ca646e74da0f16","tid":2034403,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"427170807ecb4815d2267db604c1fd046cce693c","tid":2034403,"uid":15,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"repl