,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T13:51:18.000Z","msg":"呢堆風格先係數碼暴龍特色"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T14:32:37.000Z","msg":"係 好鍾意呢種<br />\n係弱肉強食嘅世界不斷打生打死又用機械強化自己打到自己甩皮甩骨都仲要打嘅風格<br />\n<br />\n睇返啲立繪 係好強調爪 牙 機械 修補 等等<br />\n啲肌肉嘅陰影真係好正<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aT6Yr0g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaT6Yr0g.jpg&h=731bcbf0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/47jSwrX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F47jSwrX.jpg&h=f2f4368d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇返兩隻阿古獸<br />\n暴龍機版嘅阿古獸已經有種歷戰嘅感覺係度<br />\n動畫版可以為咗作畫 啲線條就相對簡單好多<br />\n<br />\n唔止阿古獸 其他係動畫版以可愛見稱嘅數碼獸<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/axL6AVN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaxL6AVN.png&h=609782e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8t6mpO8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8t6mpO8.png&h=0bffb90b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n暴龍機版入面 就連幼年期都冇咗種傻下傻下嘅感覺 有種你搞佢連手都咬甩你嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但而家嘅數碼暴龍 只係不停咁見到暴龍獸 加魯魯獸 暴龍獸亞種 加魯魯獸亞種 奧米加獸 奥米加獸亞種 奥米加獸改 似奥米加獸等等<br />\n我都知受歡迎 但不斷咁消費奧米加就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有一大堆大波波嘅女性數碼獸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖則話數碼世界入面進化係冇固定路線<br />\n但畫一大堆女女數碼獸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n天女獸係好好j阿 但一諗起佢細細個嘅時候竟然係隻狗/貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n感覺bandai其實都冇乜重視過digimon咁<br />\n只係每隔兩年又推太一出嚟賣<br />\n仲慘過道友明"},{"pid":"a9e4cbe77be58b50e40f2292a2bb684a262b005d","tid":2034403,"uid":210233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T14:48:14.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"9037b594649021474a1a2026242595562aac9265","tid":2034403,"uid":14075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7f07a4d9d74c25d152a1318956fefffdbea9330","tid":2034403,"uid":8227,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"cb505942b591b0df98aa208246f0611ef781fa5e","tid":2034403,"uid":14075,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T13:51:18.000Z","msg":"呢堆風格先係數碼暴龍特色"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T14:32:37.000Z","msg":"係 好鍾意呢種<br />\n係弱肉強食嘅世界不斷打生打死又用機械強化自己打到自己甩皮甩骨都仲要打嘅風格<br />\n<br />\n睇返啲立繪 係好強調爪 牙 機械 修補 等等<br />\n啲肌肉嘅陰影真係好正<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aT6Yr0g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaT6Yr0g.jpg&h=731bcbf0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/47jSwrX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F47jSwrX.jpg&h=f2f4368d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇返兩隻阿古獸<br />\n暴龍機版嘅阿古獸已經有種歷戰嘅感覺係度<br />\n動畫版可以為咗作畫 啲線條就相對簡單好多<br />\n<br />\n唔止阿古獸 其他係動畫版以可愛見稱嘅數碼獸<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/axL6AVN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaxL6AVN.png&h=609782e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8t6mpO8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8t6mpO8.png&h=0bffb90b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n暴龍機版入面 就連幼年期都冇咗種傻下傻下嘅感覺 有種你搞佢連手都咬甩你嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但而家嘅數碼暴龍 只係不停咁見到暴龍獸 加魯魯獸 暴龍獸亞種 加魯魯獸亞種 奧米加獸 奥米加獸亞種 奥米加獸改 似奥米加獸等等<br />\n我都知受歡迎 但不斷咁消費奧米加就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有一大堆大波波嘅女性數碼獸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj